    <body><p><seg rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
<seg rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">舌代</seg>
一、大極丸の水夫、人を殺し候由。此事ハ西郷より申来リ候ニ付、小弟宜しく引合致し置候。此度毛利、望月が下坂致し候ニ付、諸事頼置候。何のわけも無事なるべしと奉<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>存候。<lb />
一、昨日ハ御書拝見又別紙ニも大坂の町ぶれなど――より送りくれ候ニ付、其御地の御もよふ<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">能</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（よく）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>わかり申候。<lb />
<lb />
一、大極丸此頃荷物積込などもすみ候よし。然レバ彼<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">西村</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（大坂役人）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>源吉方へ頼置<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">候フラフ</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（旗カ）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>御受取被<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>成、御引替<seg type="ruby"><seg type="rb">可<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>被<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>成</seg><seg type="rp">（</seg><seg type="rt">（なさるべく）</seg><seg type="rp">）</seg></seg>候。此儀ハ別紙松井周助兄まで送り申候間、御そふだん可<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>被<seg rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</seg>下候。<lb />
<seg rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">廿五日<seg rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">龍馬</seg></seg>
　太郎殿<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</seg></p></body>
